headline: Canadians Can "Raise a Gold One" With the Launch of Bud Light's UFC Gold Edition Can
summary: Bud Light, the official beer sponsor of UFC, is giving Canadians a chance to raise a gold one, inspired by champions who have lifted a gold belt in the Octagon速, with the launch of its UFC Gold Edition can. The release comes just in time for the sport's long-awaited return to Montreal for UFC速 315: MUHAMMAD vs. DELLA MADDALENA on Saturday, May 10.
